m/community/collectors.html\">collectors</a>.\nWhat\'s in your collection?',1,0,0,0,0,0,'2007-11-11 09:59:28'),(424,'42c909c19bcafafa587713d1538288ed',150,109,'RE: hey','Hiya,<br />\nSorry it took me awhile to reply.  I got this message back when it was first recieved but I was really busy for awhile there.  Been taking time here this past week and remembered I had some messages in my inbox I had to check out.<br />\nThat\'s cool that you saw the Fanatical show that was done, they did a great job with covering my story :)<br />\nStar Wars is really cool, I have a lot of friends who are into it.  My brother is a big Star Wars fan too.  I enjoy the original three movies the best, out of the new movies I like the first one.<br />\nThanks for the welcome letter, sorry it took me so long to reply.  :)',0,1,1,0,0,0,'2007-11-11 10:28:46'),(425,'42c909c19bcafafa587713d1538288ed',109,150,'RE: RE: hey','Hey, thanks for the reply.... I actually started this summer a small side hobby of original Ninja Turtles, nothing big, just as I see I will buy kind of hobby.  I am actually really into the 1980\'s and I try to get as much toys as I can from that decade.  Star Wars is my main hobby, but I like having small side hobbys too.... and I have many small hobby\'s :o)<br />\nFANatical doesn\'t come on anymore, they just had a few episodes and they kept showing reruns and then it just stopped coming on.  This is an awsome site!  I added you to my buddies, do the same is you want.<br />\nYour collecting pal<br />\nCarson Smith',0,1,1,0,0,0,'2007-11-11 12:03:01'),(426,'0d4c58505be0b42b5fee3d0f7c12b8d6',1,194,'Welcome to Collectors\' Quest','Welcome to Collectors\' Quest - the destination place for all collectors.\nGet started by <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/collection/create.html\">adding your own collection</a> or just click around to find some great <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/collection.html\">collections</a> and <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/commu