e I tried to block it out so badly. OH! That was one that got me... this Casper\'s Scare School movie... I\'m a -huge- fan of the original movie, and when I saw the art for that movie...? I cried... and about....got sick.<br />\nJust another flick for the Dollar.<br />\nand, I\'ll be sure to do that! :D',0,1,0,0,0,0,'2008-05-05 22:36:48'),(617,'73152d9abc099d7dfe6406f06727f2ca',1,562,'Welcome to Collectors\' Quest','Welcome to Collectors\' Quest - the destination place for all collectors.\nGet started by <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/collection/create.html\">adding your own collection</a> or just click around to find some great <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/collection.html\">collections</a> and <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/community/collectors.html\">collectors</a>.\nWhat\'s in your collection?',1,1,0,0,0,0,'2008-05-09 00:14:56'),(618,'28a0b4615f9de1ef0ad5b069e63c59f7',1,564,'Welcome to Collectors\' Quest','Welcome to Collectors\' Quest - the destination place for all collectors.\nGet started by <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/collection/create.html\">adding your own collection</a> or just click around to find some great <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/collection.html\">collections</a> and <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/community/collectors.html\">collectors</a>.\nWhat\'s in your collection?',1,0,0,0,0,0,'2008-05-09 14:24:20'),(619,'d39aacc5b68752078d71ae89d0b11c78',1,567,'Welcome to Collectors\' Quest','Welcome to Collectors\' Quest - the destination place for all collectors.\nGet started by <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/collection/create.html\">adding your own collection</a> or just click around to find some great <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/collection.html\">collections</a> and <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/community/collectors.html\">collectors</a>.\nWhat\'s in your collection?',1,1,0,0,0,0,'2008-05-12 15:32:02'),(620,'233a2f78210c852f7bf192241e8174b1',567,6,'Konnich