 come online.<br />\nThanks alot on you\'re complements :)<br />\n-Matt',0,1,1,0,0,0,'2008-05-14 14:55:57'),(629,'f91799e6668a65c6677a57cdaf1c3701',537,570,'Hello, once again!','Hi again Larry...<br />\nIf you have a moment, please go into your actual sneaker collection to mark as private. I apologize if I didn\'t make that clear before, but we are looking to keep the featured collections under wraps until we launch Sneaker Week.<br />\nAs it stands now, you have your profile hidden but not your collection.  Click on \"My Stuff\" then go into your collection. You will see \"Edit Album Details\" and click on that. Then when the new page opens, scroll down to the bottom and where it says \"Make collection public\", choose no.<br />\nAgain, thanks for taking the time to join our community! Any questions, please let me know.<br />\n-Bryan Elliott',0,1,0,0,0,0,'2008-05-14 16:07:18'),(630,'a95addd2dc1d1c22bcb09e45c5efa7f5',567,6,'Hey!','Konnichiwa. so, how are you? i know, im probably getting on yor nerves. i do that kind of thing.',0,1,1,0,0,0,'2008-05-15 13:33:37'),(631,'a95addd2dc1d1c22bcb09e45c5efa7f5',6,567,'RE: Hey!','no worries.  just busy. we\'re trying to get some commerce up on the site. we figured it would be nice if we sold collectible items since people ask us about that all of the time.<br />\nwe just uploaded some new videos so check that out. more to come.',0,1,0,0,0,0,'2008-05-15 18:01:35'),(632,'2c932e3599525f536fbdeb52161c07be',1,575,'Welcome to Collectors\' Quest','Welcome to Collectors\' Quest - the destination place for all collectors.\nGet started by <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/collection/create.html\">adding your own collection</a> or just click around to find some great <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/collection.html\">collections</a> and <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/community/collectors.html\">collectors</a>.\nWhat\'s in your collection?',1,1,0,0,0,0,'2008-05-16 18:28:33'),(633,'06caa6e2c6b5d91d777e4c9dd4650da7',