nk is interesting. The only real high dollar glassware are the Pre Prohitbition glassware . I have seen some of those go well over 1000 dollars. But more glass ware sells in the 1-20 dollar area which a number pieces that can go as high as 100 dollars.<br />\r\nDepending on the age and whats printed on them could drive its value. The best world is when you find the right piece and connect it to the right collector- better yet -the right 2 or more collectors - That could drive up an Ebay bid up  pretty high. I know I have done that more than a few times on certain that I had to have. They would be fun to  see . I have over 1600 glasses in my collection but I dont have any of these brands. But I have plenty of German and French glasses.',0,1,1,0,0,0,'2009-10-11 18:05:21'),(1964,'c50ae4a753f89f2046a48ffe7abb1e69',1,1584,'Welcome to Collectors\' Quest','Welcome to Collectors\' Quest - the destination place for all collectors.\n\nGet started by <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/collection/create.html\">adding your own collection</a> or just click around to find some great <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/collection.html\">collections</a> and <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/community/collectors.html\">collectors</a>.\n\nWhat\'s in your collection?',1,0,0,0,0,0,'2009-10-11 20:33:13'),(1965,'d4822c3dff88f541bafffc81207dd896',1,1585,'Welcome to Collectors\' Quest','Welcome to Collectors\' Quest - the destination place for all collectors.\n\nGet started by <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/collection/create.html\">adding your own collection</a> or just click around to find some great <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/collection.html\">collections</a> and <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/community/collectors.html\">collectors</a>.\n\nWhat\'s in your collection?',1,0,0,0,0,0,'2009-10-12 07:31:35'),(1966,'6a4b49d71e8345124740dafc6f4d1c57',1,1586,'Welcome to Collectors\' Quest','Welcome to Collectors\' Quest - the destination place fo