s of on the site with in the next few days. As for the orb and case, I will see what I can do to find those pics.',0,1,1,0,0,0,'2009-10-31 04:17:33'),(2033,'36990c42cc663343430262751df7b702',1591,204,'Harry Potter Collectibles Book','Yes - the wall hanging and school bag would be great.  I don\'t know if I will be able to pick them up off the site though, I don\'t think the reesolution will be high enough for reproduction in the book.  Remember to set your camera on the highest resolution posible. If you could email them to me that would be best.  Let me know when you have the pics ready and I\'ll send you my email address.',0,1,1,0,0,0,'2009-10-31 10:19:56'),(2034,'9e2f81fbfc6af1597f55a7a56ea5891c',1326,1622,'collecting','Hi<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUnfortunately, I have only been able to find vintage training bras on eBay. They don\'t come up that often, and some of the Teenform ones go for as much as US$75. Ads from various magazines are quite common, and go for under US$10.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDo you have a collection?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAmy-Lynn',0,1,1,0,0,0,'2009-10-31 10:35:09'),(2035,'9e2f81fbfc6af1597f55a7a56ea5891c',1622,1326,'collecting','Oh.. I was hoping that you knew something that I didn\'t know! Ebay is about the only way I know of as well. I like to collect ones that are still in the box but they are pretty hard to find. I don\'t think I\'ve spent over maybe $15 tho. I have some ad\'s too but I don\'t really collect them.How many do you have in your collection?',0,1,1,0,0,0,'2009-10-31 12:22:00'),(2036,'782031f03b4f4314a7c216cf70a9a3e8',1,1623,'Welcome to Collectors\' Quest','Welcome to Collectors\' Quest - the destination place for all collectors.\n\nGet started by <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/collection/create.html\">adding your own collection</a> or just click around to find some great <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/collection.html\">collections</a> and <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/community/collectors.html\">collectors</a>.\n\nWhat\'s in your collection?',1,0,0,0,0,0,'2009-10-31 12:57:20'),(2037,'9e2f81fbfc6af1597f55a7a56ea5891c',1326,1622,'collecting','Well, actually, I have tried the various online vintage clothing stores, but they have nothing really on offer. I have about 15 different training bras. My faves are the Teenform and Teencharm brands though because those are the brand that I wore.. I just won a 1960 vintage Exquisite Form First Impressions training bra. I am currently looking for a Teenform Littlest Angel and a Teenform Preview. What do you have in your collection?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAmy-Lynn',0,0,1,0,0,0,'2009-10-31 14:50:02'),(2038,'5c80ec307619f002938ab42207934506',1277,1618,'s&p shakers','Please do....what are you asking for them?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBarbara',0,0,1,0,0,0,'2009-10-31 16:09:27'),(2039,'5c80ec307619f002938ab42207934506',1277,1618,'s&p shakers','If you want to send directly...my email is Barby64@optonline.net',0,0,0,0,0,0,'2009-10-31 16:09:57'),(2040,'9e2f81fbfc6af1597f55a7a56ea5891c',1326,1622,'collecting','Hi<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs I mentioned I usually try to check out all the online vintage colthing shops. I found this one ths morning. There are 3 available so I may get one to have in my collection<br />\r\n<br />\r\nhttp://www.rubylane.com/shops/pinkpoodlevintage/ilist/,cs=Clothing:Womens:Lingerie,id=1.1.2.html<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIts a 1960s Biflex Young Scene Teen Bra. 28AA<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIts quite cute. I\'ll be glad to let you know if I find anything else.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlease tell me what you have in your collection<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAmy-Lynn',0,1,1,0,0,0,'2009-11-01 11:06:07'),(2041,'9e2f81fbfc6af1597f55a7a56ea5891c',1622,1326,'collecting','hey..<br />\r\nThanks for sending me the link. It pretty unusual to find them still in the box. I never really had any luck looking at the various online stores... just ebay. I really don\'t know what all I have in my collection but i would guess there are something in the 100 range? Some are duplicates and some are the same in different sizes. <br />\r\nIf i was to summarize things i would say that most are from the late 60\'s through today. Alot of sears, penny\'s, teenform, bestform and then a variety of others. Probably all are white and most are size 34 and 36. I was looking around just now and found an old bullet bra but I don\'t think it is the type that you collect. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nhttp://cgi.ebay.com/VINTAGE-CIRCLE-STITCH-PADDED-BULLET-BRA-32A-FAMOUS-MAID_W0QQitemZ150379184026QQcmdZViewItemQQptZVintage_Women_s_Clothing?hash=item23034c3f9a<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI\'m pretty sure that the teenform bras that i have are much newer than the ones that you are looking for but i\'ll keep my eyes open for you',0,0,1,0,0,0,'2009-11-01 11:53:49'),(2042,'c00bac83dc551a577d376f8f11e172ae',1,1624,'Welcome to Collectors\' Quest','Welcome to Collectors\' Quest - the destination place for all collectors.\n\nGet started by <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/collection/create.html\">adding your own collection</a> or just click around to find some great <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/collection.html\">collections</a> and <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/community/collectors.html\">collectors</a>.\n\nWhat\'s in your collection?',1,0,0,0,0,0,'2009-11-01 12:11:37'),(2043,'9e2f81fbfc6af1597f55a7a56ea5891c',1326,1622,'collecting','Hi<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI\'d be very interested in what you might have in Teenform or Teencharm -- from the 60s and 70s since those are the brands that I wore. I am working with a friend to document their styles for a book on the history of the training bra, so I\'d love to know what you have in particular if you have some that I don\'t have and can send me scans of the front and back of the boxes<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAmy-Lynn',0,1,1,0,0,0,'2009-11-01 12:20:20'),(2044,'56be15852895580eee2f473dd13488ed',1610,1281,'Oscar cookie jar','Hello Susan:<br />\r\nThank you for getting back to me.  I am still interested in Oscar.  Let me know your preferred payment details.  I\'ll get back to you as quickly as time permits.  (I don\'t get online very much and, hence, the delay in getting back to you).  <br />\r\nThanks again <br />\r\nJen :-)',0,1,1,0,0,0,'2009-11-01 13:14:23'),(2045,'9e2f81fbfc6af1597f55a7a56ea5891c',1622,1326,'collecting','I don\'t have everything sorted out but I have Teenform style 218 and 996 and a couple of others but i\'d have to dig them out.<br />\r\nIn Teencharm, I have style 38. I have very bras in boxes but I have alot of magazine scans that I got years ago from Premium Ads.com before it closed down. I used to be in touch with someone named Martina who was putting together a book on First Bras',0,0,1,0,0,0,'2009-11-01 17:07:30'),(2046,'9e2f81fbfc6af1597f55a7a56ea5891c',1326,1622,'collecting','Yes -- I remember Premium Ads. Pammy, who ran it, passed away.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI am best girlfriends with Martina, and we work together to track things down.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI\'d be very interested in seeing the boxes for your Teenform 218 and 996, as well as Teencharm 38 -- My first training bra was a Teencharm. I can send you my email addy directly if you can send me the scan. BTW -- what are the names of those styles?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAmy-Lynn',0,1,1,0,0,0,'2009-11-01 17:26:15'),(2047,'bb9ff2a83081888bc5750b118b70357d',1621,1553,'Xtreme Figurine called Firefight','I would like to purchase this figurine if it is still available. I have the other two Xtreme Fighter Figurines, The figurine that you have would complete my collection of these.  I am a volunteer firefighter and I collect memorabilia such as firefighting, wolves, Indian figurines, etc...    My e-mail address is articwolf13@live.com.  I\'m new to Collectors\' Quest and haven\'t quite figured out how to purchase items I am interested in.  I appreciate any assitance you could give me.  Thank You for your response, patience, and assistance                                                                          