se the site to its fullest. Thank you for all of the collections you uploaded.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI wanted to let you know two things to help you with the uploads :<br />\r\n1) The thumbnail picture for your collections can be edited. So you can have it focus on the head of an animal rather than use the automatic feature which just take the center of the picture. As you can see, many of your collections are off-center.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n2) I\'m assuming that you put the little man in for sizing. I would not include him in the thumbnail though. Otherwise all of your photos look the same. Our collectors would rather see the antelopes and gazelles that you have and not the little man each time. It is easy to just crop him from the photo. If you need help on this, let me know.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBest,<br />\r\nLiz (aka slideonover)',0,0,0,0,0,0,'2010-01-29 16:16:31'),(2908,'27f8803105d49bc12f2fd7e90839d7f0',1,2369,'Welcome to Collectors\' Quest','Welcome to Collectors\' Quest - the destination place for all collectors.\n\nGet started by <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/collection/create.html\">adding your own collection</a> or just click around to find some great <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/collection.html\">collections</a> and <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/community/collectors.html\">collectors</a>.\n\nWhat\'s in your collection?',1,0,0,0,0,0,'2010-01-29 16:59:41'),(2909,'60ea6d1a9d0978972d648ef8137ea0a9',1,2370,'Welcome to Collectors\' Quest','Welcome to Collectors\' Quest - the destination place for all collectors.\n\nGet started by <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/collection/create.html\">adding your own collection</a> or just click around to find some great <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/collection.html\">collections</a> and <a href=\"http://www.collectorsquest.com/community/collectors.html\">collectors</a>.\n\nWhat\'s in your collection?',1,0,0,0,0,0,'2010-01-29 17:35:07'),(2910,'37ffc1899bbdcb31685e617bd84797e1',